    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83c\udf1f You absolutely have to see this beauty in person. I have babied this car since day one, and it is still in truly flawless, showroom condition! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. It drives like an absolute dream, and I\u2019m only parting with it because my loss is your gain. I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate how perfect it is! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
