    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit exhibits a flawless exterior finish complemented by a pristine, showroom-quality interior. Mechanically, the vehicle is indistinguishable from new, offering a peerless driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, ensuring that this remains one of the finest examples available on the market today.",
