      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. I have babied this car from day one, and it is in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it still has that fresh new-car smell! It drives like an absolute dream and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I'm looking for a quick sale, so I've priced it to move fast. Don't miss out on a ride this clean!",
