    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This exemplary specimen features a meticulously maintained 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six powerplant with Direct Fuel Injection, delivering linear power delivery across the entire tachometer. The six-speed manual transaxle offers crisp, short-throw engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its original torsional rigidity, supported by a Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) system that has been strictly serviced to factory tolerances. With zero evidence of thermal degradation in the monobloc calipers and a pristine undercarriage free of oxidation or fluid seepage, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning collector seeking peak mechanical harmony and aerodynamic integrity.",
